strings: <voice_0x01000FF1><se_low>January: That's everything! Don't miss out this time! Get me out of here, Dormago!
<voice_0x01000FF2><se_def>China: There's nowhere else to run, we've got you.
<voice_0x01000FF3><se_high>Accuracy: You promised my brother that you would pay for everything he did!
<voice_0x01000FF4><se_def>China: Then we'll get in touch with you! You can't run away from here, Dolmag!
<voice_0x01000FF5><se_high>Accuracy: You murdered my brother! We're not leaving you here to survive!
<voice_0x01000FF6><se_high>Accuracy: Now that I have found you! Advance it! All because of Alice!
<voice_0x01000FF7><se_high>Accuracy: We hope you have a good time. The final result will arrive sooner or later!
